<DESC>AMENDMENT 0001.  CLOSING DATE EXTENDED UNTIL 5:00PM 7 JUL 04.  The following questions and answers are provided:

Item 0001 Repeater-

Q: How many Watts do you need???  25 or 45 Watts  Minimum of 45 Watts

Q: How many channels??? Minimum of 100 Channels

Q: What is the minimum Db antenna you want??? 3 Db, 5 Db, 7 Db?   There is not a specific preference for a minimum decibel level.  We need a commercial antenna capable of maintaining adequate signal to noise ratio for clear signal reception.

 

Item 0002 Mobile and Base Station-

Q: How many Watts??? 25 or 45 watts Minimum of 45 watts

Q: How many channels??? Minimum of 100 channels

Q: What is the minimum Db antenna for base station???? 3 Db, 5 Db, 7 Db?  Vendors should propose commercial standard for maintaining adequate signal to noise ratio. 

 

Item 0003 GP-340 or equal-

Q: Reference earpiece with microphone- 
    Can you specify which type you would be interested in using. See Section 1, pages 5 thru 11.  The Helmet-com bone inductive head set.

What frequencies do you plan on using within the VHF band?  Plan to operate with a frequency range of 136 – 162 MHz.

 

How many channels do you think will be used?  100 channel capacity or 255 channel capacity. Ans. At least 100 channels are required.

What power output would you require? 40-50 Watts minimum.

 

What do you mean by "applicable accessories", the radio can be outfitted one of two ways: for a vehicle with all the necessary accessories OR a base station with all the necessary accessories. We are asking for 40 base stations and 300 vehicle mounted units. 

 

CLIN 0003  GP340, what accessories would you need; for example: extra battery, single unit charger, carrying case, earpiece with microphone. Ans. Spare battery, single unit charger, carrying case, earpiece with microphone.

 

CLIN 0001  GR500 repeater, do they want us to quote for an antenna and cable and a battery back-up per repeater to make a fully functioning repeater? Yes.

 

CLIN Line 0002, 300 each, VHF Communication Equipment? Mobile Radio with accessories. Motorola GM300 or equal Mobile Radio with applicable accessories. The GM300 is no longer made and has been out of production for some time now.  

 

- Power output?

- How many channels?   Should be equivalent to Motorola GM 300.

ALL REMAINING ITEMS OF THE SOLICITATION REMAIN THE SAME
